{
  "stem": "1929.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was going on while we were in this factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably about the whole duration of the Action, what the Germans called the Action.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, of course, eight days, we know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, my memory kind of fails me, but it came back a little bit is that you know, we were all under jurisdiction of the SS, you know-- even the special branch of the whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- this was not a labor camp as such.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just-- us be staying there overnight was just a temporary thing while the Action was taking place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the Action was over, we were told to go back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now the ghetto was shrunk now to just one block or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now it was fenced in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That I do remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was fenced in with barbed wire and guarded, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now when we came back, most of the people were gone, were deported.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was only like-- you know, again, there was negotiation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Jews always negotiated with the Germans-- for 2,000 legal people to stay behind to work in these factories, OK.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "However, there were probably another 2,000 or so that were hidden in the cellars and in all their different hiding place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now this I remember very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This I have very clear memory of, is that the Jewish police and the German especially-- there was one German with a big German-- black German Shepherd.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they would go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they would sniff out the hiding places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they would get the people up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they would-- lot of times they would shoot them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember shooting them right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
